OL,3,C'It would mean so much to be there':
OL,4,CFan reacts to Villa making Europa final
OL,6,FFans of Aston Villa have said they are
OL,7,Fwilling to travel to Istanbul to watch
OL,8,Fthe club in the Europa League final
OL,9,Fagainst Freiburg even if they can't
OL,10,Fget a ticket.
OL,12,FIt's after the team won 4-1 on
OL,13,Faggregate against Nottingham Forest at
OL,14,FVilla Park last night.
OL,16,FThey will now head to the Turkish city
OL,17,Fto take on Freiburg on the 20th May.
OL,19,FLucy O'Hanlon has been a season ticket
OL,20,Fholder for nine years and is really
OL,21,Flooking forward to the final.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G1/7
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
