OL,3,C'It would mean so much to be there':
OL,4,CFan reacts to Villa making Europa final
OL,6,FAston Villa has told fans that 10,758
OL,7,Ftickets have been made available for
OL,8,Fqualifying fans but with around 33,000
OL,9,Fseason ticket holders for this season,
OL,10,Fsome fans will inevitably lose out.
OL,12,FThere are a number of different ticket
OL,13,Fallocations for fans depending on
OL,14,FEuropa League matches they have been
OL,15,Fto this season.
OL,17,FThey range from 40 Euros to 240 Euros.
OL,19,FThe flights are currently more than
OL,20,F#800 from Birmingham due to demand for
OL,21,Ftickets being so high.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G3/7
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
