OL,3,C'It would mean so much to be there':
OL,4,CFan reacts to Villa making Europa final
OL,6,FThe club last got this far in a
OL,7,FEuropean competition in 1982 when they
OL,8,Fwon the European Cup.
OL,10,FFor many fans including Lucy, it's not
OL,11,Fsomething she has ever witnessed in
OL,12,Fher lifetime which makes it even more
OL,13,Fspecial.
OL,15,FShe said: "To have this journey with
OL,16,FVilla watching them week in and week
OL,17,Fout from the Championship and getting
OL,18,Fthis far now to a European final with
OL,19,Fa great team and manager is just
OL,20,Famazing.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G4/7
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,376,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37505
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F375A1778324573
OL,3,C'It would mean so much to be there':
OL,4,CFan reacts to Villa making Europa final
OL,6,F"I always had this hope in the back of
OL,7,Fmy mind that we would get this far,
OL,8,Fbut you never want to rely on it in
OL,9,Fcase you don't get through and that
OL,10,Fcan be even more crushing."
OL,12,FLucy had already booked annual leave
OL,13,Ffor the dates before Villa had beaten
OL,14,FForest and said it's such a big moment
OL,15,Ffor her club.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G5/7
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
