PN,37506
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F375A1778324573
OL,3,C'It would mean so much to be there':
OL,4,CFan reacts to Villa making Europa final
OL,6,FShe said: "Everyone wants to be around
OL,7,Fthe stadium and to experience the
OL,8,Fatmosphere and there will be lots of
OL,9,Fpeople that won't be able to get
OL,10,Ftickets that will make the journey
OL,11,Fbecause of how much this means to us.
OL,13,F"We already had a hotel booked on a
OL,14,Frefundable basis and we will find a
OL,15,Fway around the expensive flight costs
OL,16,Fin the UK, if it's a bus or a flight
OL,17,Fto somewhere else in Turkey then that
OL,18,Fis what we will do.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G6/7
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
