OL,3,C'It would mean so much to be there':
OL,4,CFan reacts to Villa making Europa final
OL,6,F"I didn't want to book everything
OL,7,Fearly and be disappointed, but I was
OL,8,Falways hopeful with Unai Emery and his
OL,9,Fexperience in Europe that we would get
OL,10,Fthis far."
OL,12,FReporting History sees journalists
OL,13,Fjoin News At Ten anchor Tom Bradby to
OL,14,Frevisit their remarkable on-the-day
OL,15,Freports of the defining events of the
OL,16,Fmodern age. Listen to the episodes
OL,17,Fbelow...
